  "lines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "Office Memorandum • UNITED STATES GOVERNMENT",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "TO : DIRECTOR, FBI DATE: September 6, 1949",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "FROM : SAC, INDIANAPOLIS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "SUBJECT: FLYING SAUCERS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "SECURITY MATTER - X",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "At this office recently to ascertain if there was any current",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "information on \"flying saucers\". He stated [REDACTED] had been in-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "structed recently to contact Dr. [REDACTED] of Decatur,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "Indiana, with reference to a flying saucer he allegedly observed",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "in the vicinity of Lake of the Woods, Canada, on or about July 1,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "1949. An FBI Agent by the name of [REDACTED] of the Omaha office",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "was alleged to have seen the same saucer.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "When [REDACTED] conversed with Dr. [REDACTED] the Dr. told him",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "that when he returned from Canada, he found himself in the midst",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "of a polio epidemic and that as a result he had read as much",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "literature as possible with respect to polio, its symptoms, [unclear]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "diagnosis, etc. Dr. [REDACTED] told [REDACTED] that in his opinion,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "the cases which were thought to be polio in the vicinity of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "Decatur, Indiana, were not polio, but possibly the result of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "uranium poisoning and that he felt the presence of flying saucers",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "had direct bearing on the polio epidemic. Dr. [REDACTED] pointed",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "out that flying saucers were observed in the Carolina's in 1948",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "and there was a polio epidemic in the vicinity at that time.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "[REDACTED] stated he had consulted one of the physicians at the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "Benjamin Harrison Air Base and had also checked the records with",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "reference to allegations concerning the sighting of flying saucers",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "and had done a little research with respect to correlating the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "presence of flying saucers and any polio epidemic. He further",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "stated that he was reporting the matter to the proper Air Force",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "authorities, Wright Field, Dayton, Ohio.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "It has also come to the attention of this office that [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "made inquiry of the Indiana University Medical School, Indianapolis,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "Indiana, where the doctors treated the entire matter as a big joke.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "[REDACTED] also stated that Dr. [REDACTED] had heard while in Canada",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "that there had been some rather strange events somewhere in the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "interior with respect to finding what might have been remains of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "flying saucers.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "The foregoing is furnished for the information of the Bureau.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "This office is taking no action in the matter.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "[REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
